      "side": 1,
      "message": "Be careful, because something like \"localhost\" can return either an [ inet, in6 ] list or [ in6, inet ] depending on system configuration, and it\u0027s likely that the core will only listen on a inet address. In the second case, you\u0027re going to test for an in6 address and always fail.\n\nThe correct behaviour is probably to try each address in succession instead.",
